track.name: Higher
comments: Can u take me higher!
Human Clay is their only good album.

From 1997 to 2003 Creed sold around thirty million units all from just three albums.During that period they were the biggest rock band around from records sold but for some reason the frontman/singer Scott Stapp made a lot of enemies and many people started hating this band mainly because of him.Ironically the players in the band minus Stapp and his massive ego found a new singer and an even greater band alter bridge and the rest is history.
